{
  "message": "Move plugins into dedicated subdirectory\n\nReorganizes the repository structure by moving all plugin directories\ninto a new `plugins/` subdirectory. This provides better separation\nbetween plugins and repository-level files.\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
  "files": [
    {
